text: Her seiþ hu mycel landes Gilebeard hæfþ on Stiþforde, þæt is on norþhealfe þam broceXXXæceres, & þa mæd þærto, &XIIon suþhealf þa broc æt þa staneXXXæcere and fowor, &XXpenege ælce geare.
Þærto is gewitnesse, Siger, Siword, Ægelnoþ, Ægelwine, Ælfstan, Godwine on Wearlea, Sælide, Baldwine, Hubeard, Ælfred , Ledbeard.
